<bibRefCitation author="Gagne, R. J. &amp; Jaschhof, M." box="[1050,1382,438,465]" pageId="81" pageNumber="82" refId="ref351007" refString="Gagne, R. J. &amp; Jaschhof, M. (2017) A catalog of the Cecidomyiidae (Diptera) of the world. 4 th edition. Digital version 2. Systematic Entomology Laboratory, Agricultural Research Service, U. S. Department of Agriculture, 762 pp." type="book" year="2017">Gagné &amp; Jaschhof 2017: 579</bibRefCitation>
